15452,Dice Butties,[],['Action / Dexterity'],"A dexterity game where players take turns stacking cards and dice.<br/><br/>Players take turns drawing a card. They then place dice on the card as to match the picture on the card. Finally the card is balanced on a communal stack in the middle of the table. Play continues to the next player.<br/><br/>When the stack collapses, the faulting player gains points from the sum of the top face of the dice touching the table. The game continues until one player earns 100 points, ending the game and making the player with the fewest points the winner.<br/><br/>Dicey comes with 22 dice and 13 cards.<br/><br/>",2004,,,
