mple rule of repeating movement, defensive fire, and attack. A fierce battle between large armies from both sides unfolds with a playable game system.<br/><br/>Number of counters:  Approximately 700 (3 sheets)<br/>Map:   Sekigahara main battlefield (full map) + Minamiguyama area (half map)<br/>Unit types: generals, samurai generals, warlords, guns, and foot soldiers / 300 to 400 men per counter<br/>Scenario: total of 8<br/>Difficulty level (5 levels, 5 is the highest):  2<br/><br/>(description from the publisher - translated and adapted)<br/><br/>",1988,,,
