18987,Sportz Dice: Tennis,[],"['Dice', 'Sports']","A dice game that has nothing in common with Tennis except the name and terminology.  The game consists of three dice which include one &quot;Serving&quot; dice and two &quot;Rally&quot; dice.  The first player rolls the &quot;Serving&quot; dice and if a &quot;Good Serve&quot; is rolled then the 2nd player rolls the &quot;Rally&quot; die trying to roll a &quot;Return&quot; result, whereupon the first player will then roll the &quot;Rally&quot; die.  This continues until one player rolls an &quot;out&quot; result.  Play continues using standard Tennis scoring rules.  Play best out of three or five sets to determine game winner.<br/><br/>",1986,,,
