r on die) is increased by 1. If the guest is a 6, they 'freak out'. Freaked-out guests are worth negative points.<br/><br/>Play ends when the last card is played. Player with the most points wins.<br/><br/>A few variants are also included in the rules.<br/><br/>",2000,,,
